thread.title_full: GoMedigap reviewed by CHERYL E SCHUPPLER

author: CHERYL E SCHUPPLER
title: CHERYL E SCHUPPLER
text:
If looking for a dynamic company that is patient, kind, knowledgeable and courteous -- look no further. The company's they represent cover a wide area of needs. There is one to fit you, your lifestyle & your pocket $$$.
Trying to select medical coverage for dental, vision, hearing,prescriptions, etc. etc. is mind boggling to say the least. Well, Miss Sarah P. took notes, asked me questions and found me 'affordable' coverage that I can live with. I am one happy, thrilled person. And for the first time, ever, I know what kind of coverage I have. And i'm saving premium money. Doesn't get any better than that. Hip hip hooray -- many thanks - much love. My friends will hear about you. Please keep up the great work and give Miss Sarah a promotion/raise. Bye!
